.modal-holder
    .modal-container
        .fa.fa-close(data-ng-click='close();')
        .row
            input(type='email' placeholder='Enter Your Email', data-ng-model='data.email')
        .submit(data-ng-click='email();') Send Email
        .card-modal
            .card-content
                h1 National Rx Card
                .company
                    h5 Free
                    span &bull;
                    h5 Fast
                    span &bull;
                    h5 Discounts

                .patient-holder
                    h6 Preferred Client
                    .row-holder
                        .row
                            h6 BIN
                            h6(data-ng-bind='member.plan.bin')
                        .row
                            h6 PCN
                            h6(data-ng-bind='member.plan.pcn')
                        .row
                            h6 GROUP
                            h6(data-ng-bind='member.plan.group')
                        .row
                            h6 PATIENT
                            h6(data-ng-bind='member.plan.patient_id')

        .legal
            p This is <b>NOT</b> insurance and is not a substitute for insurance. Discounts are available only at participating pharmacies. You pay 100% of the discount price at the pharmacy.

            p NationalRxCard&#174; is administered by NationalRxCard, LLC, located at Park City, UT: <a href='mailto:info@nationalrxcard.com'>info@nationalrxcard.com</a>

#panel(data-ng-show='display')